Articles.Content: So I finally decided to head to minmus and decided to do a similar mission to my first trip to the mun. This meant that I tried to send a small space station along with a small lander, this time though for minmus I decided to try my first robotic lander. Things went well, for the most part. Hope you guys enjoy the mission vid, and of course I would love any suggestion (especially regarding the engine choice on my lander probe)
